{
  "stem": "15694.11",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was sit-- my father was sitting with the back, near the door, by was back, to the outside, on a-- on a stool.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a man was working on him, operating.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was such a noise, the din from the people who-- who searched my comrades, that I could not understand what he was saying or rather, answering when I said the-- the funny-- asked a funny question, how-- how you're doing or something, you know?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was absolutely unnecessary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I wanted to have some kind of a conversation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I could see sideways, like a smile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was like, reassured.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went on, into my-- into my wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Got in my corner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And not many people inside the wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The weather was nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I managed, somehow, to open-- I don't know how, to open the tin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was meat, corn beef, fat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Something my body hasn't known for how-- how long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I was very, very careful not to sling it down with one tiger sling.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I sort of ate it little bit at a time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I also wanted to save some for my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And every now and again, an ever-shorter distance of time, if I may say that way, I had another nibble, another nibble.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then to the great shock, I found that I was nearly at the end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And instead of giving it to my father whom I-- maybe I could help him, the doors were closed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And later on, I couldn't pass it on to him anymore anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I had great reproaches later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because the next day, somebody came into my-- opened the door in the morning and called my name.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
